headline: 3 Internet Software Stocks to Buy From a Prospering Industry
summary: The Zacks Internet software industry participants like ANET, MNDY and PCTY are benefiting from high demand for SaaS due to the increasing need for hybrid work, learning and diagnosis software, as well as cybersecurity applications.
